programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: Hundreds of beautiful and talented women converge on AT&T Stadium to start the hardest audition process in professional sports, trying out for a coveted spot on the most famous NFL cheerleading squad in the world, the Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: With the field narrowed down to 119 women, the pressure is on. They must quickly learn a power pom routine and the famous kickline in order to perform it an hour later before the judges.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: The veterans finally enter the audition process. Now all 83 women are judged head to head during a panel interview, a solo dance performance and on their appearance on the football field as seen and the big screen.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: First, the ladies need to have the "classic look" of a Dallas Cowboys Cheerleader. Kelli's hair and make-up transformations are legendary. The ladies are also assessed through a new state of the art fitness test, "Styku".

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: Kelli media trains the rookie candidates to determine who best represents the DCC at press events. NBC news anchor, Meredith Land tests their on-camera interview skills.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: Personality is critical when representing the DCC brand. Kelli takes the women on location to see how they interact during a public appearance.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: Katy Perry's choreographer, Nick Florez, stops by to offer some performance advice to the ladies. A day that each cheerleader never forgets. The first time they wear the DCC uniform to pose for their cameo photos.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: The squad goes on an appearance to support pop music star, Demi Lovato. The ladies learn the entrance to the famed pre-game dance. It's a make or break moment. If a woman can't learn it quickly it might be her last night.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: With two suspended vets, the team must re-block their formations for their Hall Of Fame performance. New vets step up as a new point of the triangle is named. The rookie candidates try to get their footing during this never seen before rehearsal.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: 23 veterans travel to Canton, Ohio to perform at Jerry Jones' induction to the Pro Football Hall of Fame. All eyes are watching as the DCC perform for the NFL elite.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: In the finals audition, the competition really heats up. Now, surviving candidates must go head-to-head against experienced veteran cheerleaders for a coveted spot in the DCC Training Camp.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: Training Camp begins! The newly elected training camp candidates are excited, even star-struck, as they meet the veterans for the first time at Valley Ranch.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: The group competes in a grueling army fitness test to try and earn the privilege of being on the elite "Power Squad." At that evening's rehearsal, the first cuts will be made.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: The rookies are given "makeovers" to transform them into the image of a DCC.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: The entire squad needs a wake-up call and guest choreographer Kitty Carter gives it to them.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: The final dance rehearsal of week 7 has a surprise guest judge who puts everyone on edge. Ultimately, in Kelli's office, the tears flow as some dreams surprisingly come to an end.

programme.title: Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders: Making the Team
programme.desc: Join 65,000 screaming Cowboys fans as the cheerleaders hit the turf and wow the entire stadium and themselves during their first Dallas Cowboys football game of the season.

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico
programme.desc: (S1E8) After the DEA closes in on Rafa's enormous pot field, Félix tries to stop his associates from retaliating. Kiki and Jaime meet with investigators.

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico

programme.title: Narcos: Mexico
programme.desc: (S1E10) As pressure mounts, Félix returns to Sinaloa. An enraged Jaime and Mika seek justice and answers.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E1) Chilean drug chemist Cockroach brings his product to Colombian smuggler Pablo Escobar. DEA agent Steve Murphy joins the war on drugs in Bogota.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E2) Communist radical group M-19 makes a move against the narcos, while Murphy gets an education in Colombian law enforcement from his new partner Peña.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E3) Murphy encounters the depths of government corruption when he and Peña try to derail Escobar's political ambitions by proving he's narco.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E4) Despite a new extradition treaty, the U.S. puts more money into fighting communism, creating new challenges for Murphy and Peña in the hunt for Pablo.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E5) Pablo's extreme methods put the narcos on the brink of war with Carillo and the government. Peña tries to protect his witness.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E6) Peña and Carillo close in on Gacha. Murphy tries to protect pro-extradition candidate Gaviria from a notorious assassin connected to Pablo.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E9) Pablo is reunited with an estranged family member. Judy Moncada's life is put in danger. The DEA and CIA clash over how to handle Los Pepes.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S2E10) Javier deals with repercussions from Judy's interview. Tata tries to convince Pablo to surrender for the sake of the children.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E1) The Gentlemen of Cali gather their associates together for a big surprise announcement about the future of their business.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E2) A gas incident threatens to destroy the agreement between Cali and the government and requires Jorge's help. Peñahas problems with his old contact in Los Pepes.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E3) The Rodríguez brothers are hiding during the negotiations. Pacho meets the Lord of the Heavens in Mexico. Peña's new DEA team visits Cali.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E4) Peña hatches a plan to try to capture Cali leader Gilberto Rodriguez. Amado proposes a business idea to Pacho.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E5) Paranoid about leaks, Miguel cracks down on his security. Pacho makes a decision about his new offer. Peña works on cultivating a witness.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E6) Jorge takes a dangerous risk. An accident in New York threatens to expose Chepe. Peña travels to Curacao to arrest a potential witness.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E7) Peña plans another secret operation to topple a member of the Cali cartel but may run out of time while looking for him.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E8) David seeks revenge on behalf of his father and puts Enrique in danger. Peña asks Don Berna for help on a rescue mission.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E9) David follows his suspicions. Peña is shocked to discover the depth of corruption in the Colombian government. Miguel is sought after once again.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E10) David and Peña are in a race against each other to find Pallomari. Peña makes a serious decision about the future of his career.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S3E10) David y Peña están en una carrera para encontrar a Palomari. Peña toma una decisión importante sobre su futuro.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E1) El químico chileno conocido como "la cucaracha" le ofrece su producto al narcotraficante colombiano Pablo Escobar. El agente de la DEA Steve Murphy se une a la guerra contra las drogas en Bogotá.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E2) El grupo comunista radical M-19 se enfrenta a los narcos, mientras Peña le enseña a Murphy las reglas del juego de acuerdo con las leyes colombianas.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E3) Murphy y Peña se topan con la gigantesca corrupción del gobierno colombiano cuando intentan detener las ambiciones políticas de Escobar, probando que es un narco.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E4) Pese a un nuevo tratado de extradición, los Estados Unidos están más interesados en combatir el comunismo que en atrapar a Escobar. Murphy y Peña se enfrentan a nuevos obstáculos.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E5) Los métodos extremos de Pablo ponen a los narcos al borde de una guerra con Carrillo y el gobierno. Peña trata de proteger a sus testigos.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E6) Peña y Carrillo acorralan a Gacha. César Gaviria, un candidato pro-extradición es acechado por un asesino de Escobar y Murphy trata de protegerlo.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E7) Cuando sus ambiciones políticas fracasan, Pablo Escobar decide esconderse, no sin antes vengarse de sus enemigos. Murphy y Peña finalmente obtienen ayuda de la CIA.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E8) Un trágico error obliga al gobierno a cambiar la estrategia contra Escobar. Sin embargo, el mayor peligro para Pablo está dentro de su propia organización.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E9) La cacería por Pablo parece llegar a su fin después de hacer un pacto con el gobierno, pero Murphy, Peña, y el Cartel de Cali, tienen otros planes.

programme.title: Narcos
programme.desc: (S1E10) Las actividades de Pablo desde la prisión hacen que el gobierno tome acciones extremas. Murphy y Peña se enfrentan a un problema diferente.

programme.title: Narcos
